The paper focuses on analysing the contribution of image data to sentiment analysis, which suggests a strong connection to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of models that combine both data types also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the mention of label embeddings suggests a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM).
